  "content": "# Multi-Spoke Spawning: Verified (2026-03-28)\n\nSpawned test spoke container from hub devcontainer. Full stack works:\n- Auth: .credentials.json via host path mount = authenticated\n- Repo: Fresh git clone --depth 1 works. Worktrees fail (absolute .git paths)\n- Network: Spoke reaches hub at http://app:8020 via compose network\n- MCP: corvia_system_status returned live data from spoke\n\nDocker-from-Docker: bind mounts must use HOST paths. Resolve via docker inspect $(hostname).\nDecision: fresh clone over worktrees for container isolation.\n\n## Inference Crash Pattern (corvia-dev restart)\nAfter corvia-dev restart, inference process loads embedding + chat models, then crashes (exit 1) ~4s after chat model loads. Restarted process starts gRPC server but never reloads models. Root cause: likely race condition during rapid restart cycles. Clean restart after settling resolves it.",
